{
  "stem": "17001.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So one day, they selected us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when they selected us-- All three of you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All four of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All four of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then we felt that must be a good place because they locked up the door on the barrack.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was the Lola, the Lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was the four Blockalteste who was with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said to my sister Clara that we must be going in a good place because otherwise they would know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They wouldn't be there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was no more that you have to go to the kitchen with the [HUNGARIAN] to get the food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow they brought it in, and they bought us potatoes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Cooked potatoes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Boiled potatoes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this German [GERMAN] was the one who was throwing it up on every [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as many people were there, that's how many people had to share the potatoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And unfortunately, we were on the top because I didn't want all that lice to fall on me, and all the cysts to come on me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I always liked to go on the top.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the-- the potatoes fell right between the slit because of nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So maybe I would have like one or two potatoes left over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So next day when we were getting the potatoes again, so I put out my dress that she should put the potatoes on it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She gave me a bang on my head.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought it's going to fell off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she throw the potatoes on the-- on the [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So vicious, you know, but so vicious that it-- it's just unbearable.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing I know that they-- we weren't allowed to go out from the barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
